{"tid":1546794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！白宮聯署集合！要求通過人權及民主法案！","createTime":"2019-09-06T12:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T00:53:36.000Z","uid":124309,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"453670a2aaa98c26d6d40f7c6b01cc3500bbc97f","tid":1546794,"uid":124309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:10:35.000Z","msg":"美國國會就嚟開會，非常緊急，唔好講嘢，同我簽晒佢！白宮聯署已經翻嚟啦！<br />\n<br />\n1. 美國國會下星期一9月9號開會，聯署要求美國唔好俾林鄭呃，通過香港人權及民主法！十萬個都唔好停，請繼續簽，簽到五十萬一百萬！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=3b2cdb3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-say-no-carrie-lams-so-called-concessions-continue-call-us-pass-hk-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 反對曾偉雄出任聯合國職位聯署！上次系統有問題唔到數，今次再簽！香港人心不死！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=2c39138c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 大陸越嚟越離譜，壓迫國泰，主席都要辭職，好可能要迫國泰賣晒比國航！我哋聯署要求美國杯葛大陸航線，因為政治干預航空係恐怖主義！請幫幫手，救救國泰！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/aviation-safety-please-boycott-chinese-airlines-china-now-threatens-cathay-pacific-politics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Faviation-safety-please-boycott-chinese-airlines-china-now-threatens-cathay-pacific-politics&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=7327182b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/aviation-safety-please-boycott-chinese-airlines-china-now-threatens-cathay-pacific-politics</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-urge-beijing-government-stop-interfering-cathay-pacific-and-possibly-other-private-companies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-urge-beijing-government-stop-interfering-cathay-pacific-and-possibly-other-private-companies&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=71d839e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-urge-beijing-government-stop-interfering-cathay-pacific-and-possibly-other-private-companies</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 要求美國不再輸出高科技給中國作人面識別！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/investigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Finvestigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=97e8831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/investigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 831是恐怖主義！要求美國將香港政府列為恐怖主義機構！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=f4398ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 中國公安假扮香港警察，要求美國通過民主及人權法案！呢個仲有三日，欠三萬個簽名!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/chinese-police-impersonating-hong-kong-police-officers-anti-extradition-bill-protest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fchinese-police-impersonating-hong-kong-police-officers-anti-extradition-bill-protest&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=aa5736a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/chinese-police-impersonating-hong-kong-police-officers-anti-extradition-bill-protest</a>"},{"pid":"54e4df4a673b762a81219205705b15b35bacc681","tid":1546794,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce53e16cadcc5deb33c9b9e18ac7f5a3ad6dd2c1","tid":1546794,"uid":48556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:11:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64b31a9c2ff6f63a088fb82b7b95a0129379b983","tid":1546794,"uid":124309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"0f57d5a6c901211bebb8a41e31da0984e23a74d4","tid":1546794,"uid":197086,"l