titions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Finvestigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=97e8831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/investigate-restrict-us-companies-support-communist-chinas-high-tech-mass-surveillance-terrorism-acts</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 831是恐怖主義！要求美國將香港政府列為恐怖主義機構！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=f4398ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 中國公安假扮香港警察，要求美國通過民主及人權法案！呢個仲有三日，欠三萬個簽名!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/chinese-police-impersonating-hong-kong-police-officers-anti-extradition-bill-protest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fchinese-police-impersonating-hong-kong-police-officers-anti-extradition-bill-protest&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=aa5736a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/chinese-police-impersonating-hong-kong-police-officers-anti-extradition-bill-protest</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00154bf2f4219fa6b256b36bf160aa5ca7ebbe85","tid":1546794,"uid":284480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca988c6a365ffada7df7c473f1ad0f28b84353dc","tid":1546794,"uid":124309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:27:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bb01f87be0becb17637f906ad118a82671032c8d","tid":1546794,"uid":17399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:29:39.000Z","msg":"全部已簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d52e0cdb829459e84891b81200f131c7451a22c","tid":1546794,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"已經簽哂, 不過繼續push"},{"pid":"a165d2e7e33b57ef5a9de9b79b85effc84b91959","tid":1546794,"uid":15391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:41:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cedb93811cd576d488fc2ab1a71195411774b2c9","tid":1546794,"uid":258550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51278215ac5a5fa816e8091384e0b92c74c79df3","tid":1546794,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:48:27.000Z","msg":"All signed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da546fef73b60ebc2343238cbc143bfc2fe4bfc6","tid":1546794,"uid":145664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:49:43.000Z","msg":"907 機場攻略(濃縮版)<br />\n無時無刻緊記自己普通市民/旅客身份<br />\n<br />\n- 一定要提早到機場！ 最好十二點已經係機場<br />\n- 市民/旅客裝，唔着黑色衫，唔叫口號，可以戴普通口罩，唔需要其他裝備<br />\n- 地點: 暢達路巴士總站 或者 暢航路<br />\n- 交通: 優先搭巴士入，建議大家首先 集合左係青馬收費廣場 再搭巴士入機場，機場快線去 香港站<br />\n- 青馬收費廣場係交通樽頸，如果所有途徑巴士都要埋站會好影響交通；同樣，香港站一停，機鐵就送唔到遊客去機場<br />\n- 如果巴士唔停青馬收費廣場就直接入機場；如果直接停A同E機場巴士服務，旅客要搭巴士入機場就唯有 去東涌<br />\n- 策略: 到左機場唔一定要企定等， 緊記市民/旅客身份 ，可以係周圍行行企企，排下隊，落車上車<br />\n<br />\n- 無論如何都唔好係 T1/2 機場客運大樓附近設路障塞路 ，即使有任何行動都一定要 等到三點 後全部人入左機場先<br />\n<br />\n關於清場/逃走路線<br />\n- 無時無刻緊記自己普通市民/旅客身份 ，萬一警察真係清場，記得 緊貼其他遊客 ，佢地去邊大家就去邊， 普通市民/旅客冇犯法係唔需要逃走 <br />\n- 有咩合理原因可以係機場範圍出現？接機/送機，參觀機場，巴士/地鐵愛好者，即興旅行，等等<br />\n<br />\n- 密切留意睇Telegram頻道: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=6a134909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n機場Fact Check Channel: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/fcairport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffcairport&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=ec64e597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fcairport</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjFkzL9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjFkzL9.png&h=b1adcf9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SGvWZu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SGvWZu.png&h=3dddac2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ja1jcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ja1jcQ.png&h=4ae2cb47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UpztJEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpztJEv.jpg&h=bbc66c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsPQWZv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsPQWZv.jpg&h=d8769fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUH7eMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUH7eMb.jpg&h=f486c2cd&s={SIZE}